data.header: How to remove the 3 photo limit
How to remove the 3 photo limit

data.description:
If you are using an iOS device (iPhone or iPad), you need to pay for your subscription in the app: 
 
 1. Open the application and select the "Subscription" section or "Subscribe" on the menu.
 
 2. Choose a subscription type and make sure it fits your needs. 
 
 3. Confirm payment by following the instructions on the screen.
